# Anchor to the repo root so this only ignores a top-level scratch
# `data/` directory. An unanchored `data` pattern also matches the
# in-package resource directory `src/eia/data/`, which silently keeps
# the `eia.data` package (routes.yaml / recipes.yaml) out of git, every
# clone, CI and the published wheel.
